#home-page
	.jumbotron
		h1.display-4 Baker Points
		h3 Check-In

		p.lead
			| Please enter your phone number to log in and receive points.

		.alert.alert-danger(ng-cloak, ng-show="errorMessage") {{errorMessage}}

		form(ng-submit="checkNumber()")
			.form-group
				label.hidden Phone Number
				input.form-control.form-control-lg(
					field-validate="errors",
					name="phone-number",
					ng-model="login.phone",
					type='text',
					placeholder='000-000-0000'
				)
			.btn-group
				button.btn.btn-success.btn-lg Submit

		hr
		p
			| Not registered?
		p.lead
			a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='#', ui-sref="app.register") Register